title: Sawbones: Black Salve
description:
Would you believe that the hot new (very old) alternative medicine paste that indiscriminately burns your cells off is bad for you? We know, we were shocked too.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
